title: I got 149X rank in pessat can I get CSE AI ML ?

comments.body: The cutoffs for last year were posted here sometime back, search and see.
Will that cutoff increase or decrease?

That cannot be exactly predicted , it depends on the number of seats(I heard they have increased it) , number of people attending the counseling session .
I would expect a increase in cutoffs due to huge increase in fees and increase in number of seats .
1.5k rank AIML in RR campus might be close in the first round . You might get in EC campus.
Is there any placement difference in EC campus and RR campus for CSE?
no both sit for same companies..

Hi
I am sure you would have got a seat in RR campus of you would have chosen it
One of my friends did with rank 151X.

PS even I got a seat in the same course and my rank is near yours in RR campus
